text = "<Translating...>

<Begin Data Upload>


Sf'arl has done it. The [Insane Genius?] he is.

Stars have become [Immaterial?]

The universe has always been our dominion, our [labyrinth?] to design.

With [The Collapsing Fire?] we have unlocked the key to our next frontier.



Beyond the echos of [The waves?], the [Wise ones?] have beckoned to us.

This is our answer.






We shall break the boundaries that have been imposed on us by [Ancient?].

We shall break our curse.






<End Data Upload>"

