text = "<Translating...>

<Begin Data Upload>


There is a dreamer.

He walks the paths of the world, awake. Yet he still dreams. Dreams of futures, of pasts. 

We have a name for you.


A name for the dreamer, the sleeper, and the one who is awake.

But they shall not know it, for it is only the ones who are awake who can tell who the others are.


We are awake.

Beyond space and time we see all.


What shall the dreamer choose?


To open his eyes and follow the road set out by the ones who are awake?


Or continue dreaming?




<End Data Upload>"

